      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·鄭風·001.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">Tsze Î.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>緇衣之宜兮，敝，予又改為兮。適子之館兮，還，予授子之粲兮。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>How well do the black robes befit you!
When worn out, we will make others for you.
We will go to your court,
And when we return from it, we will send you a feast!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
