        <seg>緇衣之好兮，敝，予又改造兮。適子之館兮，還，予授子之粲兮。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>How good on you are the black robes!
When worn out, we will make others for you.
We will go to your court,
